_sText:
This map is made by Falo and Säm

Säm gave me the idea and made the basics.
And i did everything else.

1 Terrorist spawn
23 CT spawns

IMPORTANT: you must set mp_autoteambalance 0  and mp_limitteams 0 
to play this map.

This maps idea is that the terrorist  must run to the other side of the map while all the ct's are trying to shoot him. And if the terrorist gets to the other side then he can shoot or blow up all the ct's.

i thought that this was an awesome idea so i hope you like it ;)
